PathOfBuilding.Notes:
Hi, there!
Some Notes on Flasks: >Lavianga's is the SAFEST. You can take more stacks and hits. >Chalice is the FASTEST. You have more uptime on your other flasks. >Don't forget to quality all flasks!
Some Notes on Timeless Jewels: >Mana Regen and Effect of Non-Curse Auras is great, but extra. >If you can only afford one mod, go for the Effect of Non-Curse Auras for Grace. >It HAS to be VENARIUS though! Don't buy the wrong one!
Some Notes on Gear: >You do not have to be resistance capped. You should try, though. >Try to have at least positive Cold and Lightning. >Implicit on belt is useless, buy one with MS% on Flask, +All Res%, or Grace Effect. >Save the $$ and don't pay for the quality corrupted Indigon. You don't use ES anyways.
Some Notes on Leveling: >I just tried to brute force it with OOS/WOC/LST and it was miserable. Doable, but miserable. >You'll probably be happier leveling however you like then regret orb the shit out of everything.
Some Notes on Darkness Running: >It may take a bit to get used to using the Mana Flask so much. >I tap the Enduring Flask every time I refresh Phase Run. This seems to work. >At high stacks tap Lavi's with increasing frequency until you decide to log/die. >Even if SC vs. HC, the logout to character screen macro is super nice.
Some Notes on Treasure: >Do NOT break walls, ever. EVER. Don't give up a profitable pathway for short term greed. >Do not waste time on minor boxes. Turn on highlighting to see box names asap. >Prioritize Fossils, Resonator Nodes, and Wealth nodes. Ignore all others. >Fossils are obvious. Resonators have what looks like soundwaves resonating from them. GET IT. HAH. >Pick up Flares as you see them, saves on surface time.
Some Shameless Self-Promotion: >Bite-Sized Guide: https://tinyurl.com/y5lhgjcb >Main Builds Page: https://tinyurl.com/y5vwayk2 >Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/brittleknee >Twitter: https://twitter.com/brittlekneetv >Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brittlekneetv/
